snippet.title: Bounding Into Comics
snippet.description:
Bounding Into Comics is a news and entertainment website with a focus on comic book movies and TV. We routinely cover Marvel Studios, DC Comics, Star Wars, Star Trek, Ghostbusters, Disney, and more.

Not only do we look at comic book movies and TV, but we also touch on the latest in anime and video games. We cover everything from The Rising of the Shield Hero and Dragon Ball to the latest video games from Blizzard, EA, Ubisoft, Nintendo, and others.

We host a weekly YouTube livestream called Bounding Live! where we discuss the current news in entertainment and routinely feature guests. Bounding Live! airs on Wednesdays at 9 PM ET.

We also host a rotating review show, where we are currently reviewing Cowboy Bebop. That show normally airs every Friday at 7 PM ET.

We also routinely upload the newest movie trailers through our license with EPK.TV.

Email: jftrent@boundingintocomics.com
